The paper proposes a new algorithm for deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The algorithm involves maximizing entropy and exploring the environment effectively, which are topics related to robotics and control (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions benchmark control tasks, which may involve computer vision (cs.CV) in some cases.
